  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may increase the time required to place a trap by 2 steps (a move becomes a full-round, a standard becomes 1 round, and a full-round becomes 1 minute) and increase the DC of placing the trap by 5. Doing so allows you to apply a second (dart) talent to a dart trap or a second (snare) talent to a snare trap. Alternatively, you may place a dart and snare trap in the same space to be triggered simultaneously. If you possess the Trap Wielder talent and combine it with this ability, resolve each trap separately.</p>\n",
